flowchart TD
    STOP["Stop Event<br/>(user clicks Stop)"]
    HOOK["validate-wardley-math.sh"]
    CHECK_CMD{"/arckit.wardley<br/>command?"}
    FIND_FILE["Find latest WARD file<br/>in projects/*/wardley/"]
    EXTRACT_OWM["Extract OWM code blocks"]
    EXTRACT_TABLES["Extract Component Inventory"]
    VALIDATE_COORDS["Validate coordinates<br/>[0,1] range"]
    VALIDATE_STAGES["Validate stage-evolution<br/>alignment"]
    VALIDATE_SYNTAX["Validate OWM syntax"]
    CROSS_CHECK["Cross-check OWM vs Tables"]
    PASS["Allow Stop"]
    FAIL["Block Stop<br/>Show errors"]
    
    STOP --> HOOK
    HOOK --> CHECK_CMD
    CHECK_CMD -->|No| PASS
    CHECK_CMD -->|Yes| FIND_FILE
    FIND_FILE --> EXTRACT_OWM
    FIND_FILE --> EXTRACT_TABLES
    EXTRACT_OWM --> VALIDATE_COORDS
    VALIDATE_COORDS --> VALIDATE_STAGES
    VALIDATE_STAGES --> VALIDATE_SYNTAX
    VALIDATE_SYNTAX --> CROSS_CHECK
    EXTRACT_TABLES --> CROSS_CHECK
    CROSS_CHECK -->|All pass| PASS
    CROSS_CHECK -->|Failures| FAIL
